org.apache.commons.pool.impl

类 FairGenericObjectPool

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.pool.BaseObjectPool
      • org.apache.commons.pool.impl.GenericObjectPool
        • org.apache.commons.pool.impl.FairGenericObjectPool
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.apache.commons.pool.ObjectPool

    public class FairGenericObjectPool
extends GenericObjectPool
    Version of GenericObjectPool which is 'fair' with respect to the client threads using borrowObject. Those which enter first will receive objects from the pool first.
    另请参阅:
    GenericObjectPool
